<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV41">
<l>eṉṟumpuṉ vāṭai yitukaṇ ṭaṟitumiv vāṟuvemmai</l>
<l>yoṉṟu muruvuñ cuvaṭun teriyila mōṅkacurar</l>
<l>poṉṟum vakaipuḷḷai yūrvā ṉaruḷaru ḷātavinnāḷ</l>
<l>maṉṟiṉ ṉiṟaipaḻi tūṟṟiniṉ ṟemmaivaṉ kāṟṟaṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Always the mean north wind. Seeing it we will know. We didn’t know</l>
<l>a heat of this kind, and form and taste. These days when no grace comes</l>
<l>from the one who rides the bird in a manner that high Asuras perish,</l>
<l>constantly spreading full blame on the village common, the strong wind will kill me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
